    "description": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >《Dream Bar Simulator》是一款新一代模拟经营游戏，在游戏中你将扮演一名小镇酒吧老板。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" style=\"text-align: center\"><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3174950/extras/c2d39ff5504aebd07c27a420115bca83.webp?t=1771850647\" width=319 height=59 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" style=\"text-align: center\"><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3174950/extras/2e16c17a451c314184e7f0fe3d228fc5.poster.avif?t=1771850647\" width=600 height=320 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3174950/extras/2e16c17a451c314184e7f0fe3d228fc5.webm?t=1771850647\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3174950/extras/2e16c17a451c314184e7f0fe3d228fc5.mp4?t=1771850647\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >你可以从多种现有配方中打造自己的菜单，或自行创作全新饮品。调制高品质的饮品，让顾客保持满意。高品质的饮品会带来更开心的顾客、更丰厚的小费，以及更好的酒吧声誉。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" style=\"text-align: center\"><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3174950/extras/2db44a4e1eb348e637dbb0a5237350a5.webp?t=1771850647\" width=319 height=59 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" style=\"text-align: center\"><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3174950/extras/43755c6ee9e317afdbe18928c4195dc2.poster.avif?t=1771850647\" width=600 height=320 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3174950/extras/43755c6ee9e317afdbe18928c4195dc2.webm?t=1771850647\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3174950/extras/43755c6ee9e317afdbe18928c4195dc2.mp4?t=1771850647\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >在《Dream Bar Simulator》的世界中，你将发现丰富多样的资源，确保酒吧始终货源充足。从各种酒类和消耗品到家具和装饰品，你可以根据情况选择在线订购或在本地采购。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" style=\"text-align: center\"><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3174950/extras/6df4f8e83b713f14ef35cf269d026f07.webp?t=1771850647\" width=319 height=59 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" style=\"text-align: center\"><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3174950/extras/5e81365a4cbbc53d9aeb58a91288296c.poster.avif?t=1771850647\" width=600 height=320 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3174950/extras/5e81365a4cbbc53d9aeb58a91288296c.webm?t=1771850647\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3174950/extras/5e81365a4cbbc53d9aeb58a91288296c.mp4?t=1771850647\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >让你的梦想酒吧成为现实！通过强大的自定义工具展现你独特的创意愿景，打造理想的氛围，吸引你想要的顾客群体。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" style=\"text-align: center\"><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3174950/extras/e32482c3fcb7bf28f8dfadb956b4f94d.webp?t=1771850647\" width=319 height=59 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" > </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" style=\"text-align: center\"><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3174950/extras/bb31b3250b0770bb0cf21e8be1b9ceb7.poster.avif?t=1771850647\" width=600 height=290 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3174950/extras/bb31b3250b0770bb0cf21e8be1b9ceb7.webm?t=1771850647\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3174950/extras/bb31b3250b0770bb0cf21e8be1b9ceb7.mp4?t=1771850647\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >随着你的酒吧生意兴隆，扩展你的版图！提升接待容量，赚取更多利润，成为全城最火爆的场所。 </p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >核心特色</h2><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >海量饮品与原材料选择</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >创作原创鸡尾酒配方</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >多种饮品复杂度等级，带来额外挑战</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >设计独特菜单，展现酒吧风格</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >招募拥有独特性格与背景故事的员工（开发中）</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >深度酒吧自定义选项</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >维持秩序与清洁（或者随你所愿！）</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >应对醉酒顾客以及偶尔发生的酒吧斗殴！（开发中）</p></li></ul>",
